      "id": "sorting",
      "title": "Sorting / 排序",
      "frequency": "not-frequent",
      "frequency_label": "Not Frequent",
      "description": "将元素按升序排列。铜级题目通常不需要 O(N log N) 排序算法——重复取最小值 O(N²) 即可。",
